sequenceDiagram
    participant Manager as Organization owner/admin
    participant Member as Authenticated organization member
    participant API as Marketplace API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL with forced RLS
    participant Mod as Global marketplace admin
    Manager->>API: Submit review after install/purchase
    API->>DB: Verify ownership and upsert pending review
    API->>DB: Write tenant audit event
    Mod->>API: Publish or reject review
    API->>DB: Update moderation state and audit
    Member->>API: Submit abuse report with evidence
    API->>DB: Insert moderation-queue record
    alt Critical severity
        API->>DB: Persist unread admin notification and audit it
    end
    Mod->>API: Investigate, resolve, or dismiss
    API->>DB: Update queue state and acknowledgement
